Title: Andrews E226 pilot assembly CSC
Description: A genuine Andrews spare, this pilot assembly is compatible with Ecoflam and CSC boilers. A pilot assembly normally includes a pilot bracket, injector, electrode and thermocouple. The pilot flame operates alongside the printed circuit board (PCB) and the rest of the pilot assembly for safe and efficient ignition.
